  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK998">
<l>naṇpāṟṟā rāki nayamila ceyvārkkum</l>
<l>paṇpāṟṟā rātal kaṭai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is wrong (for the wise) not to exhibit (good) qualities even towards those who bearing no friendship (for them) do only what is hateful.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
